<a name="角色介绍" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">蓝色大海的传说</span>角色介绍</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="4" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="anchor-list">
<a name="juesejieshao" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="lemmaWgt-roleIntroduction">
<ul>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item ">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E8%93%9D%E8%89%B2%E5%A4%A7%E6%B5%B7%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%A0%E8%AF%B4/19701126/0/f31fbe096b63f6247e5e25fe8e44ebf81b4ca3cf?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss1.bdstatic.com/-vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D611%2C49%2C682%2C971%3Bw%3D138%3Bq%3D95/sign=c0079fcd33f33a878a225a5afb6a2109/f31fbe096b63f6247e5e25fe8e44ebf81b4ca3cf.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B2%88%E6%B8%85/20163521" data-lemmaid="20163521">沈清</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%85%A8%E6%99%BA%E8%B4%A4">全智贤</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
地球上处于灭绝危机的美人鱼，身体干涸的话就会长出腿来，会心灵感应，具有通过身体接触来抹除人类记忆的能力。因为一场事故而来到了陆地上，见到了第一个人类，回到大海之后对那个男人产生了无限的思念，为了遵守再次和他相见的约定，再次重返陆地，可偏偏她坚信不疑的那个家伙是坏人中最坏的，是个邪恶的骗子。
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item ">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E8%93%9D%E8%89%B2%E5%A4%A7%E6%B5%B7%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%A0%E8%AF%B4/19701126/0/faf2b2119313b07eb6c984f405d7912396dd8cd2?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss0.bdstatic.com/-4o3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D556%2C0%2C785%2C1118%3Bw%3D138%3Bq%3D95/sign=eb944088a4345982d1c5bfd231c1049b/faf2b2119313b07eb6c984f405d7912396dd8cd2.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%AE%B8%E4%BF%8A%E5%AE%B0">许俊宰</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%9D%8E%E6%95%8F%E9%95%90">李敏镐</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
<div>外貌帅气，头脑也好使，只要采取骗子策略并付诸果敢的行动力就能百分百成功。从韩国科学技术院中途退学成为世界顶级智商俱乐部门萨盟的会员，是个能完美变身任何职业的天才骗子。虽然行骗，但有自己的行骗哲学和道德观念。人生目标是找到妈妈并把攒下的所有钱都给她。某一天，被一个他说什么谎话都相信的懵懂女闯进了人生。</div><div></div><div></div><div></div>
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item ">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E8%93%9D%E8%89%B2%E5%A4%A7%E6%B5%B7%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%A0%E8%AF%B4/19701126/0/b3b7d0a20cf431ade099482f4236acaf2edd9858?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss3.bdstatic.com/-Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D20%2C102%2C605%2C860%3Bh%3D195%3Bq%3D95/sign=27820f8bc2ef76092844c3df13ef93e0/b3b7d0a20cf431ade099482f4236acaf2edd9858.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
金聃龄
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%9D%8E%E6%95%8F%E9%95%90">李敏镐</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
朝鲜时代从汉阳来到江原道歙谷县的新任县令。途遇天灾暂住当地富商杨氏的旅舍，因缘巧合救下被抓捕的人鱼世华。后来得知自己与世华儿时相识，本彼此爱慕却无法相守，少年时的他依父母之命另娶他人，新婚之夜为了再见世华跳入海中，被世华救起并被抹去了关于她的记忆。几经周折相认后开始带着世华躲避杨氏的追捕危机。
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item ">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E8%93%9D%E8%89%B2%E5%A4%A7%E6%B5%B7%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%A0%E8%AF%B4/19701126/0/ac345982b2b7d0a249641360c2ef76094a369a99?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss1.bdstatic.com/-vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D415%2C15%2C455%2C647%3Bw%3D138%3Bq%3D95/sign=fca8b99d46c2d562e6478aadda25a1da/ac345982b2b7d0a249641360c2ef76094a369a99.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
赵南斗
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%9D%8E%E7%86%99%E4%BF%8A/64142" data-lemmaid="64142">李熙俊</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
有着浓重的方言口吻，笑容爽朗，极具亲和力，可以让任何人在十分钟内放下戒心。打得了高尔夫，玩得了扑克，下得了围棋，唱歌、声音模仿、舞蹈也通通不在话下，不管是洋酒、烧酒还是啤酒全都能喝，而且喝不醉。骗俊宰的大学学费不成反而成功说服他与自己合伙，带领俊宰走进了诈骗的世界。
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item ">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E8%93%9D%E8%89%B2%E5%A4%A7%E6%B5%B7%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%A0%E8%AF%B4/19701126/0/7af40ad162d9f2d36c6df313a0ec8a136227ccca?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss3.bdstatic.com/-Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D425%2C33%2C660%2C938%3Bw%3D138%3Bq%3D95/sign=740bc2684f2309f7f320f7524f3a3ec6/7af40ad162d9f2d36c6df313a0ec8a136227ccca.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
泰武
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%94%B3%E5%8E%9F%E6%98%8A">申原昊</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
沉默寡言的花美男黑客，被俊宰的一句“全世界网速最快的地方”轻松勾搭到韩国并暂时定居下来。在黑客和伪造等技术方面无人能及，不管是钥匙还是什么，只要经过他的手便一定能够解开，是个万能终结者。
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item ">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E8%93%9D%E8%89%B2%E5%A4%A7%E6%B5%B7%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%A0%E8%AF%B4/19701126/0/a2cc7cd98d1001e969cf03f2b10e7bec55e7975f?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss0.bdstatic.com/94o3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D345%2C0%2C469%2C665%3Bw%3D138%3Bq%3D95/sign=cee125c521381f308a56d7e99432783d/a2cc7cd98d1001e969cf03f2b10e7bec55e7975f.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
许致贤
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%9D%8E%E7%9F%A5%E5%8B%8B/20250125" data-lemmaid="20250125">李知勋</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
原名尹致贤，因为母亲再婚改变户籍成为许致贤，也就是俊宰名义上的哥哥。刚进家门就得忍受俊宰对他的敌意，直到俊宰离家出走前他对俊宰说了非常讽刺的话。当他怀着负罪感靠近善良的妈妈，却发现其实妈妈并不如他想象中的那么善良，妈妈邪恶的笑容让他明白了要在妈妈面前当个乖儿子就得成为这个世界上的恶魔。
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item more">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E8%93%9D%E8%89%B2%E5%A4%A7%E6%B5%B7%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%A0%E8%AF%B4/19701126/0/78310a55b319ebc4fc06ebc48b26cffc1e171674?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss3.bdstatic.com/-Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D373%2C0%2C491%2C698%3Bw%3D138%3Bq%3D95/sign=426075395f4e9258b27bdcaea1b1e66b/78310a55b319ebc4fc06ebc48b26cffc1e171674.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
姜瑞熙
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%BB%84%E6%96%B0%E6%83%A0">黄新惠</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
十分懂得利用人们的同情来假装善良的女人。孤儿出身，高中毕业后辗转工厂干活，结过两次婚，两次都因丈夫婚后不幸离世令她得到了数亿元的保险金，她用这笔钱生活的悠然自得。然而她并不满足，又开始觊觎高中同学的丈夫，利用手段最终登堂入室成为了俊宰的继母，得悉俊宰的父亲打算让俊宰当继承人之后，又策划了第三次不幸。
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item more">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E8%93%9D%E8%89%B2%E5%A4%A7%E6%B5%B7%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%A0%E8%AF%B4/19701126/0/aec379310a55b319a15f1f284aa98226cefc17cc?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss2.bdstatic.com/9fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D404%2C28%2C415%2C587%3Bw%3D138%3Bq%3D95/sign=0076861e82d4b31ce473cefbbae2174b/aec379310a55b319a15f1f284aa98226cefc17cc.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
许日中
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%B4%94%E6%94%BF%E5%AE%87">崔政宇</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
<div></div><div>陆军士官学校高级干部出身的房地产商，在击退好几个竞争者后成功追求到牟裕兰并与其结婚，生下儿子俊宰。可好景不长，渐渐对裕兰产生疲倦的时候遇见了天使般的瑞熙，很快为之沉沦。离婚的那一刻他失去了很多，包括最疼爱的俊宰。随着时间的流逝，他开始思念俊宰母子，所以下定决心，找到俊宰挽回一切，而此时却发生了不幸。</div>
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item more">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E8%93%9D%E8%89%B2%E5%A4%A7%E6%B5%B7%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%A0%E8%AF%B4/19701126/0/6a63f6246b600c3398e7ca35134c510fd8f9a1b4?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss3.bdstatic.com/7Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D185%2C0%2C785%2C1118%3Bw%3D138%3Bq%3D95/sign=3a8ef5e72134349b604934c5f4db2dfb/6a63f6246b600c3398e7ca35134c510fd8f9a1b4.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
牟裕兰
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%BD%97%E6%98%A0%E5%A7%AC">罗映姬</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
<div>有钱人家的独生女，从小养尊处优。俊宰出生后她的父母相继去世，因为错写担保将遗产全搭了进去。与丈夫离婚后，她没要一分抚慰金骄傲的离开了，将儿子留给前夫望其好好抚养。她的位置被高中同学瑞熙取而代之，为了让姜瑞熙善待俊宰，一直遵守着儿子成年之前不再出现的承诺。目前她正在车诗雅哥哥嫂子家做着住家帮佣的工作。</div><div></div>
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item more">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E8%93%9D%E8%89%B2%E5%A4%A7%E6%B5%B7%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%A0%E8%AF%B4/19701126/0/9358d109b3de9c825904da726581800a18d843ed?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss0.bdstatic.com/94o3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D204%2C49%2C779%2C1109%3Bh%3D195%3Bq%3D95/sign=46478bdbf4faaf5190acdbffb166a4da/9358d109b3de9c825904da726581800a18d843ed.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
