</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%94%B3%E6%83%A0%E5%96%84">申惠善</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
<div></div><div>韩国科学研究院（KAIST）的研究员，许俊宰的大学同学，集美貌与智慧于一身，是众多女生的标榜。她逻辑严谨，行事果断，七年来一直暗恋俊宰。充满自信地以为俊宰会爱上自己，直到沈清出现，一直端庄的她开始出现了表情的变化。</div>
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item more">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E8%93%9D%E8%89%B2%E5%A4%A7%E6%B5%B7%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%A0%E8%AF%B4/19701126/0/5fdf8db1cb1349547f8bfc995f4e9258d0094ab1?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss2.bdstatic.com/-fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D42%2C0%2C974%2C1384%3Bh%3D195%3Bq%3D95/sign=2d1de8271cce36d3b64bd97007c708ab/5fdf8db1cb1349547f8bfc995f4e9258d0094ab1.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
